com.joliciel.talismane

Class Talismane

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.Talismane

  • public class Talismane
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for processing a stream of data using a reader via analyse(Reader), and creating various outputs, with formats as defined by the configuration, with their location specified in the constructor.

    The processing will go from getStartModule() to getEndModule(). Not thread-safe.

    Processing will stop when the reader finishes reading, or when three consecutive TalismaneSession.getEndBlockCharacter() are encountered.

    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
